description: MeMeDAO, like Ark Invest or Tuttle Capital Management in real life, is a relatively well-known DAO project which focuses on investing in promising startup cryptocurrency teams. The goal of MeMeDAO is to allow everyone in the blockchain world to enjoy the dividends of cryptocurrencies.
